<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>Management Bot</title>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/common.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/bot.css">
	<script src="../js/jquery-3.2.1.min.js"></script>
	<script src="../js/jquery-ui.min.js"></script>
	<script src="../js/jquery.form.min.js"></script>
	<script src="../js/vue.min.js"></script>
	<script src="../js/lodash.min.js"></script>
	<script src="../js/calendar.js"></script>
	<script src="../js/common.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="pop_wrap" style="width:480px;">
		<div class="pop_tit">
			<p>개인정보 수정</p>
		</div>
		<div class="pop_cont">
			<div class="g_table02">
				<table>
					<caption>내 사진, 비밀번호, 이메일 주소 등 개인 정보 확인 및 수정하는 표 입니다.</caption>
					<colgroup>
						<col style="width:130px;">
						<col>
					</colgroup>
					<tbody>
						<tr>
							<th>내 사진 변경</th>
							<td>
								<div class="my_photo_chg">
									<span class="photo" style="background-image:url('../images/common/img_profile.png')"></span>
									<div class="ctrl">
										<input type="file" id="photo_upload" class="ir">
										<label for="photo_upload">사진업로드</label>
										<button class="del">사진삭제</button>
									</div>
								</div>
							</td>
						</tr>
						<!-- 17.12.09 수정 -->
						<tr>
							<th>현재 비밀번호</th>
							<td><input type="password" class="full"></td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<th>변경 비밀번호</th>
							<td><input type="password" class="full"></td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<th>변경 비밀번호 확인</th>
							<td><input type="password" class="full"></td>
						</tr>
						<!-- // 17.12.09 수정 -->
						<tr>
							<th>이메일주소</th>
							<td>
								<input type="text" class="full" value="test@nextlab.co.kr">
							</td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<th>휴대전화번호</th>
							<td>
								<div class="mobile_num">
									<select name="" id="">
										<option value="">010</option>
									</select>
									<span class="bar">-</span>
									<input type="text">
									<span class="bar">-</span>
									<input type="text">
								</div>
							</td>
						</tr>
					</tbody>
				</table>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="btn_wrap">
			<button class="g_btn01">적용</button>
			<button class="g_btn02" onclick="hidePopupLayer(); return false">닫기</button>
		</div>
	</div>
	<script>
		setPopup(2);
	</script>
</body>
</html>